Makefile commands :

-- ALL: --
all        - make all outputs (ps/pdf files in output/)
	     does not leave dvi or eps files.

-- GRAPHICS: --
eps        - make all eps graphics

-- DVI FILES: --
dvi        - make guide dvi files (build/guides/xxx.dvi)
exdvi      - make exercise dvi files (build/ex/xxx.dvi)
instrdvi   - make instruction dvi files (build/instr/xxx.dvi)
bookdvi    - make book dvi files (build/book/xxx.dvi)


-- OUTPUT --
standalone - make guide ps/pdf files (output/guides/)
exercise   - make exercises ps/pdf (output/exercise/)
instr      - make instruction-set ps/pdf (output/instr/)
book       - make book ps/pdf (output/book/)

-- CLEAN --
clean      - remove everything including intermediate files
